import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Switch, Route, Redirect } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Layout } from 'antd'

import SettingNav from '../../components/setting-nav'
import User from './user'
import MessageSetting from "./message";

const { Sider, Content } = Layout

export default class Setting extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Layout>
                <Sider theme="light" className="setting-sider"><SettingNav /></Sider>
                <Layout className="setting-content">
                    <Content>
                        <Switch>
                            <Route exact path="/setting" component={User} />
                            <Route exact path="/setting/message" component={MessageSetting} />
                            <Redirect to="/setting" />
                        </Switch>
                    </Content>
                </Layout>
            </Layout>
        )
    }
}
